reviewText: Love the Berenstain Bears & how they cover the important things.
Love this series. Great, moral teachings presented in a clean way!
Just good clean fun. Enjoyable to watch and easy for kids to follow along. Story line is engaging and up beat.
I love these movies! Great for the whole family!

A great family show. This DVD contains the following episodes:

1- Visit Fun Park
2- Go to the Movies
3- Gotta Dance
4- White Water Adventure
5- Papa's Pizza
